<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 15:11:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>团结一致的中国回族哀悼在地震中丧生的女孩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/tight-knit-chinese-hui-ethnic-minority-mourns-loss-girl-quake-2023-12-21/</link><description>周四，中国西北地震灾区杨洼村的回族社区正在哀悼八岁的马金媛，她在家中睡觉时，墙体倒塌，她在墙体废墟下丧生。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 14:49:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/tight-knit-chinese-hui-ethnic-minority-mourns-loss-girl-quake-2023-12-21/</guid></item><item><title>美国启动半导体供应链审查以促进国家安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-launching-semiconductor-supply-chain-review-boost-national-security-2023-12-21/</link><description>美国商务部周四表示，将对美国半导体供应链和国防工业基础展开调查，以解决来自中国芯片的国家安全担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 14:46:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-launching-semiconductor-supply-chain-review-boost-national-security-2023-12-21/</guid></item><item><title>美国和中国高级军事官员周四发表讲话——五角大楼声明</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-china-top-military-officials-spoke-thursday-pentagon-statement-2023-12-21/</link><description>美国参谋长联席会议主席周四上午与中国同行进行了通话，美国参谋长办公室称，美国和中国恢复了军事通信。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 13:50:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-china-top-military-officials-spoke-thursday-pentagon-statement-2023-12-21/</guid></item><item><title>捷克亿万富翁蒂卡奇从中信收购布拉格斯拉维亚足球俱乐部</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/czech-billionaire-tykac-buying-soccer-club-slavia-prague-chinas-citic-report-2023-12-21/</link><description>捷克亿万富翁帕维尔·蒂卡奇和他的团队周四表示，他将从中国投资集团中信集团手中收购国内顶级足球俱乐部布拉格斯拉维亚队。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 12:26:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/czech-billionaire-tykac-buying-soccer-club-slavia-prague-chinas-citic-report-2023-12-21/</guid></item><item><title>解说：中菲关系还能恶化到什么程度？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/how-far-could-china-philippines-relations-worsen-2023-12-21/</link><description>尽管中国和菲律宾都呼吁通过对话解决该战略航道的紧张局势，但双方都加大了捍卫南海领土主权的言论。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 11:47:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/how-far-could-china-philippines-relations-worsen-2023-12-21/</guid></item><item><title>Morning Bid：这是为了圣诞节欢呼吗？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2023-12-21/</link><description>Alun John 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 11:02:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2023-12-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国以国家安全为由禁止出口稀土加工技术</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-bans-export-rare-earths-processing-technologies-2023-12-21/</link><description>作为全球最大的稀土加工国，中国周四禁止出口提取和分离战略金属的技术，进一步保护其在几种战略金属中的主导地位。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 10:53:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-bans-export-rare-earths-processing-technologies-2023-12-21/</guid></item><item><title>缅甸军政府因应对叛军进攻而被指控犯有战争罪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-junta-accused-war-crimes-over-response-rebel-offensive-2023-12-21/</link><description>国际特赦组织周四表示，缅甸军方在打击少数民族叛乱分子的过程中可能对平民进行了不分青红皂白的袭击，并使用了违禁的集束弹药，并呼吁对涉嫌战争罪进行调查。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 09:15:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-junta-accused-war-crimes-over-response-rebel-offensive-2023-12-21/</guid></item><item><title>惠誉将万达商业评级下调至“限制性违约”，随后升级至“CC”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/fitch-downgrades-wanda-commercial-restricted-default-then-upgrades-cc-2023-12-21/</link><description>不良债务置换完成后，惠誉评级将大连万达商业管理集团的评级从“C”下调至“限制性违约(RD)”，同时将该公司从“RD”升级至“CC”，以反映其重组后的状况。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 08:52:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/fitch-downgrades-wanda-commercial-restricted-default-then-upgrades-cc-2023-12-21/</guid></item><item><title>中菲关系：南海争端重大事件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/rift-deepens-between-philippines-china-over-south-china-sea-2023-12-21/</link><description>在菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯的领导下，马尼拉和北京之间的关系恶化，马尼拉转向支持菲律宾与中国的海上争端的美国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 07:56:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/rift-deepens-between-philippines-china-over-south-china-sea-2023-12-21/</guid></item><item><title>在具有里程碑意义的安全案件中，香港维权律师被拒绝保释</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/bail-denied-hong-kong-rights-lawyer-landmark-security-case-2023-12-21/</link><description>香港一家法院周四驳回了亲民主活动人士兼律师周恒东的新保释申请，根据中国实施的国家安全法，周恒东的颠覆罪审判预计将于 2024 年底开始。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 06:24:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/bail-denied-hong-kong-rights-lawyer-landmark-security-case-2023-12-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国煤矿事故已造成12人死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-coal-mine-accident-kills-12-2023-12-21/</link><description>据中央电视台周四报道，中国东北省份黑龙江省一处煤矿发生事故，已造成 12 人死亡。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 06:00:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-coal-mine-accident-kills-12-2023-12-21/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院判处资深劳工活动人士的妹妹监禁六个月</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-jails-sister-veteran-labour-activist-six-months-2023-12-21/</link><description>香港一家法院周四判处一名亲民主工会领导人的妹妹六个月监禁，原因是在这座中国统治的城市正在进行的安全镇压期间，她从后者的家中带走了证据。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 04:02:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-jails-sister-veteran-labour-activist-six-months-2023-12-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国警告菲律宾不要在南海问题上“误算”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-warns-philippines-resolve-south-china-sea-tensions-via-dialogue-2023-12-21/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅警告菲律宾，南海争端升级中的任何误判都将招致坚决回应，并敦促通过对话解决两个邻国之间的“严重困难”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 03:14:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-warns-philippines-resolve-south-china-sea-tensions-via-dialogue-2023-12-21/</guid></item><item><title>台湾指责中国在取消关税后实施经济胁迫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-keeps-up-pre-election-trade-pressure-taiwan-with-tariff-cut-removals-2023-12-21/</link><description>台湾周四指责中国经济胁迫和选举干涉，此前北京宣布结束对台湾部分化学品进口的关税削减，并称台北违反了一项贸易协议，就在台湾大选之前。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 03:07:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-keeps-up-pre-election-trade-pressure-taiwan-with-tariff-cut-removals-2023-12-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>